Package: ny.gov
Title: New York State Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for New York State Socrata Open Data portal (data.ny.gov).
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for crime, MTA finances, bridge
    conditions, salaries, real estate licenses, lottery, and more.
